name: MILK

description.en: MILK is a utility token for Udder Chaos, a Solana NFT project. The project focuses on creating sustainable ways to reduce the circulating supply of MILK. Udder Chaos has a Solana validator, RPC rentals, raffles and NFT rentals to drive the value for MILK.
